Legal Identifier:
- Identifier must start with a letter, a currency character($) or a connecting character such as underscore.
- Identifier cannot start with a digit!!

Source File Declaration Rules
- There can be only one public class per source code file.
- If there is a public class in a file. the name of the file must match the name of the public class
- a file can have more than one non public class.
- file with no public class can have a name that does not match any of the classes in the file.


